data.description: Wonderful New construction home in Gray's Creek/Cypress Lakes community. This home boast 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. Master bedroom and laundry room are on the main floor. Master has lots of windows to let in the sun light, master bath has beautiful tiled shower/glass door, garden tub, separate toilet area. Formal dining room, beautiful kitchen, Upstairs you will find a great loft space for family time and 3 bedrooms. Gutters, blinds included and a large lot. Family friendly neighborhood.
